396
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:43,250
<font size="64">You are a real dessert lover.</font>

397
00:09:43,250 --> 00:09:44,390
<font size="64">Don't you want to eat this?</font>

398
00:09:44,190 --> 00:09:47,830
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(The Bread Lover grabs one of every variety.)</font>

399
00:09:44,390 --> 00:09:45,790
<font size="64">I picked this one.</font>

400
00:09:45,790 --> 00:09:47,690
<font size="64">- They have different tastes. - They do.</font>

401
00:09:48,660 --> 00:09:49,860
<font size="64">This is...</font>

402
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:51,360
<font size="64">Are you sure you can eat them all?</font>

403
00:09:53,260 --> 00:09:57,000
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Dong Hyun is worried that they might spend all the money.)</font>

404
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:55,870
<font size="64">- There are so many good things. - I know.</font>

405
00:09:56,970 --> 00:09:58,500
<font size="64">We'd end up spending 500 dollars.</font>

406
00:09:58,500 --> 00:10:00,070
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Don't worry.)</font>

407
00:09:58,500 --> 00:09:59,600
<font size="64">It won't happen.</font>

408
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:02,110
<font size="64">They have cake here too!</font>

409
00:10:02,870 --> 00:10:04,780
<font size="64">- I know. - You picked too many.</font>

410
00:10:05,180 --> 00:10:07,140
<font size="64">- Let's just eat. - Wait. Hang on a second.</font>

411
00:10:07,140 --> 00:10:08,780
<font size="64">- This is a lot. - If you eat lunch after this,</font>

412
00:10:08,780 --> 00:10:10,210
<font size="64">- we will spend 500 dollars. - Right.</font>

413
00:10:10,210 --> 00:10:11,780
<font size="64">- All right. - This is too much.</font>

414
00:10:11,380 --> 00:10:14,220
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Anxious)</font>

415
00:10:11,780 --> 00:10:12,780
<font size="64">- It's too much. - Or...</font>

416
00:10:12,780 --> 00:10:14,190
<font size="64">Do you want me to get rid of some of them?</font>

417
00:10:14,190 --> 00:10:16,420
<font size="64">- Let's get this one. - Buy this one. Americano.</font>

418
00:10:16,420 --> 00:10:18,390
<font size="64">- It's 20 dollars for 10 Americanos. - That sounds good.</font>

419
00:10:16,550 --> 00:10:19,290
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(He gets worried sick as they add coffee.)</font>

420
00:10:19,020 --> 00:10:20,760
<font size="64">- The ube drink sounds good. - It's over 100 dollars.</font>

421
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:21,930
<font size="64">It's over 100 dollars then.</font>

422
00:10:21,930 --> 00:10:23,230
<font size="64">You should buy it with your own money.</font>

423
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:25,430
<font size="64">Let's get 1 coffee for every 3 people.</font>

424
00:10:25,430 --> 00:10:26,460
<font size="64">Come on.</font>

425
00:10:26,460 --> 00:10:28,170
<font size="64">- Who does that these days? - We can't share our drinks.</font>

426
00:10:26,630 --> 00:10:30,840
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(The people buzz at the suggestion of sharing coffee.)</font>

427
00:10:28,170 --> 00:10:29,170
<font size="64">- But we never finish our coffees. - Director,</font>

428
00:10:29,170 --> 00:10:30,970
<font size="64">500 dollars isn't enough for a cafe.</font>

429
00:10:30,970 --> 00:10:33,300
<font size="64">I can spend 500 dollars by myself at a cafe.</font>

430
00:10:33,340 --> 00:10:35,940
<font size="64">Then, we will have iced Americanos.</font>

431
00:10:35,940 --> 00:10:36,940
<font size="64">Iced Americano.</font>

432
00:10:36,940 --> 00:10:38,480
<font size="64">- Five. - Four.</font>

433
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,780
<font size="64">- Four Americanos. - Four.</font>

434
00:10:39,780 --> 00:10:41,080
<font size="64">And one ube drink?</font>

435
00:10:39,980 --> 00:10:43,510
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Treasurer Yu remains level-headed.)</font>

436
00:10:41,180 --> 00:10:43,510
<font size="64">- And one ube drink. - We should try this one.</font>

437
00:10:43,510 --> 00:10:45,380
<font size="64">- Did you order four Americanos? - One, two, three, four...</font>

438
00:10:45,380 --> 00:10:46,720
<font size="64">Did you order a decaf coffee too?</font>

439
00:10:46,820 --> 00:10:48,250
<font size="64">Please make one of them decaf.</font>

440
00:10:48,390 --> 00:10:50,150
<font size="64">- All right. - Decaf.</font>

441
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:52,060
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(The two want decaf coffee.)</font>

442
00:10:50,150 --> 00:10:51,760
<font size="64">- We will have a decaf. - Good.</font>

443
00:10:52,060 --> 00:10:54,230
<font size="64">- I want a decaf, too. - But it costs an extra dollar.</font>

444
00:10:54,230 --> 00:10:56,760
<font size="64">- Just drink the cheap one. - Just drink it.</font>

445
00:10:56,760 --> 00:10:58,060
<font size="64">Just take one for the team...</font>

446
00:10:58,060 --> 00:10:59,560
<font size="64">- and skip some sleep. - A dollar is big.</font>

447
00:10:59,860 --> 00:11:01,070
<font size="64">Right.</font>

448
00:11:01,130 --> 00:11:03,030
<font size="64">How could you tell us to skip some sleep?</font>

449
00:11:03,030 --> 00:11:04,440
<font size="64">- He already paid. - Just skip some sleep.</font>

450
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:05,800
<font size="64">- It's over. - We can play games...</font>

451
00:11:05,070 --> 00:11:08,170
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Sensitive)</font>

452
00:11:05,800 --> 00:11:07,640
<font size="64">- and make more money. - He's right about that.</font>

453
00:11:07,740 --> 00:11:09,510
<font size="64">- Why are you so upset? - What do we do then?</font>

454
00:11:09,510 --> 00:11:10,640
<font size="64">Isn't that simple?</font>

455
00:11:09,910 --> 00:11:12,280
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(My decaf coffee...)</font>

456
00:11:10,640 --> 00:11:12,210
<font size="64">We can't guarantee that we will win.</font>

457
00:11:12,210 --> 00:11:14,580
<font size="64">The production crew is making us look like bad people.</font>

458
00:11:12,580 --> 00:11:15,980
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Conflict caused by decaf coffee)</font>

459
00:11:14,580 --> 00:11:17,820
<font size="64">- We don't know if we will win. - The rules are ridiculous.</font>

460
00:11:17,920 --> 00:11:19,220
<font size="64">"I hate people."</font>

461
00:11:18,680 --> 00:11:20,890
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(He brings out his secret weapon.)</font>

462
00:11:19,580 --> 00:11:20,920
<font size="64">Let's just go out.</font>

463
00:11:20,920 --> 00:11:22,250
<font size="64">- Let's go. We don't know it yet. - Let's just get out.</font>

464
00:11:21,390 --> 00:11:25,120
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(If this keeps up, will Dong Hyun be able to get a gift?)</font>

465
00:11:22,250 --> 00:11:23,990
<font size="64">- Let's go. - It's on me.</font>

466
00:11:23,990 --> 00:11:26,260
<font size="64">- Come on out. - They make us look bad.</font>

467
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:29,260
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Total spending: 63 dollars, Amount left: 437 dollars)</font>

468
00:11:26,260 --> 00:11:27,660
<font size="64">Just come on out.</font>

469
00:11:27,730 --> 00:11:28,960
<font size="64">Not bad.</font>

470
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,960
<font size="64">Why do you make us look like bad people?</font>

471
00:11:29,760 --> 00:11:33,630
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(The guests get sheepish after loading up on bread.)</font>

472
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:33,230
<font size="64">- We aren't bad people. - All right.</font>

473
00:11:33,230 --> 00:11:35,830
<font size="64">If you succeed in the mission later, you can multiply it up to fivefold.</font>

474
00:11:33,700 --> 00:11:36,930
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(They will get the chance to multiply it up to 5 times!)</font>

475
00:11:35,830 --> 00:11:36,930
<font size="64">- Right. - We can multiply it.</font>

476
00:11:36,930 --> 00:11:40,940
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(So far)</font>

477
00:11:36,930 --> 00:11:38,870
<font size="64">We have over 400 dollars now.</font>

478
00:11:38,940 --> 00:11:40,810
<font size="64">Five times that amount is a huge sum.</font>

479
00:11:40,870 --> 00:11:43,470
<font size="64">Hang on. I get all that,</font>

480
00:11:43,470 --> 00:11:45,340
<font size="64">but I just wanted a decaf.</font>

481
00:11:45,340 --> 00:11:46,840
<font size="64">How could you tell me to skip on some sleep instead?</font>

482
00:11:47,180 --> 00:11:48,850
<font size="64">It's only one more dollar.</font>

483
00:11:48,850 --> 00:11:51,420
<font size="64">Can't you just spend an extra dollar?</font>

484
00:11:51,420 --> 00:11:52,720
<font size="64">- We have 500 dollars. - Jong Kook.</font>

485
00:11:52,850 --> 00:11:54,950
<font size="64">Jong Kook, here's a dollar for your decaf coffee.</font>

486
00:11:54,690 --> 00:11:57,920
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Here you go.)</font>

487
00:11:55,490 --> 00:11:57,860
<font size="64">You should get me a coffee instead of a dollar.</font>

488
00:11:57,860 --> 00:11:58,920
<font size="64">- I want a decaf. - It's coming.</font>

489
00:12:01,160 --> 00:12:02,560
<font size="64">This is on the house.</font>

490
00:12:01,330 --> 00:12:05,860
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(The desserts bought with their precious money are served.)</font>

491
00:12:02,660 --> 00:12:04,860
<font size="64">Mimi looks really excited now.</font>

492
00:12:06,860 --> 00:12:10,730
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(An eye-catching selection of baked goods...)</font>

493
00:12:07,030 --> 00:12:08,600
<font size="64">This looks delicious.</font>

494
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:10,130
<font size="64">This is amazing.</font>

495
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:13,900
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(and the leading dessert of the Gen Z, purple ube latte)</font>

496
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:12,170
<font size="64">- This is the ube drink. - The orange...</font>

497
00:12:12,170 --> 00:12:14,170
<font size="64">It is taking over the dessert world these days.</font>

498
00:12:13,900 --> 00:12:15,610
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(And coffee that is not decaf.)</font>

499
00:12:14,170 --> 00:12:15,610
<font size="64">This is nice.</font>

500
00:12:15,610 --> 00:12:18,940
<font size="64">- The bingsu is on the house. - Really?</font>

501
00:12:16,210 --> 00:12:20,010
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Even the bingsu that was on the house!)</font>

502
00:12:18,940 --> 00:12:20,480
<font size="64">You don't have to pay for it.</font>

503
00:12:20,540 --> 00:12:22,480
<font size="64">I should stop talking and eat this.</font>

504
00:12:23,550 --> 00:12:24,750
<font size="64">- Right. - What's wrong?</font>

505
00:12:24,880 --> 00:12:26,280
<font size="64">This is too small.</font>

506
00:12:26,280 --> 00:12:27,620
<font size="64">The coffee is too small.</font>

507
00:12:28,150 --> 00:12:29,290
<font size="64">Mimi, here's your ube.</font>

508
00:12:30,150 --> 00:12:32,120
<font size="64">Look at how many straws I'm sticking in a cup.</font>

509
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:33,620
<font size="64">- The coffee is... - That's such a waste.</font>

510
00:12:32,390 --> 00:12:33,420
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Piled up)</font>

511
00:12:33,420 --> 00:12:35,660
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(The straws stick out like a diffuser.)</font>

512
00:12:33,620 --> 00:12:35,490
<font size="64">We never finish the coffee anyway.</font>

513
00:12:35,490 --> 00:12:37,930
<font size="64">I don't do this even with my family.</font>

514
00:12:37,930 --> 00:12:40,130
<font size="64">Who shares a drink like this?</font>

515
00:12:40,130 --> 00:12:41,300
<font size="64">That's exactly why we're doing this.</font>

516
00:12:41,300 --> 00:12:42,730
<font size="64">- We're not family. - But this is...</font>

517
00:12:41,500 --> 00:12:43,900
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Miraculous reasoning)</font>

518
00:12:43,270 --> 00:12:44,400
<font size="64">I know.</font>

519
00:12:45,270 --> 00:12:46,470
<font size="64">- All right. - This is a lot.</font>

520
00:12:46,470 --> 00:12:48,640
<font size="64">Who wants to try the ube drink?</font>

521
00:12:48,640 --> 00:12:49,870
<font size="64">- What's ube? - Ube.</font>

522
00:12:48,740 --> 00:12:51,380
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(The dazzling purple ube latte)</font>

523
00:12:49,870 --> 00:12:50,910
<font size="64">Sweet potato.</font>

524
00:12:51,710 --> 00:12:53,810
<font size="64">- How does it taste? - Mimi.</font>

525
00:12:53,740 --> 00:12:55,350
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Sipping)</font>

526
00:12:53,880 --> 00:12:56,010
<font size="64">- This is good. - It's delicious.</font>

527
00:12:57,310 --> 00:12:59,250
<font size="64">- Do you like it? - They make a good ube.</font>

528
00:12:59,780 --> 00:13:01,590
<font size="64">- Which one did you use? - I used this one.</font>

529
00:13:00,950 --> 00:13:02,520
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Mimi's straw)</font>

530
00:13:02,450 --> 00:13:04,390
<font size="64">- It's okay to use the same straw. - All right.</font>

531
00:13:04,460 --> 00:13:07,190
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Tasting what the youth of today likes)</font>

532
00:13:04,490 --> 00:13:06,390
<font size="64">She's right. It's okay.</font>

533
00:13:09,460 --> 00:13:10,960
<font size="64">I know, but...</font>

534
00:13:09,660 --> 00:13:12,130
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(He picks up his coffee after trying the ube drink.)</font>

535
00:13:12,030 --> 00:13:14,470
<font size="64">Try the ube. But it has only two straws.</font>

536
00:13:12,160 --> 00:13:14,670
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(It doesn't seem to be the old man's cup of tea.)</font>

537
00:13:15,470 --> 00:13:17,030
<font size="64">- This is good. - Let me try.</font>

538
00:13:15,530 --> 00:13:19,100
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Ssaebssaeb tries it as well.)</font>

539
00:13:17,170 --> 00:13:20,400
<font size="64">It tastes like milk tea, right?</font>

540
00:13:20,240 --> 00:13:22,510
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Smacking)</font>

541
00:13:20,800 --> 00:13:22,340
<font size="64">Exactly. It's like taro milk tea.</font>

542
00:13:22,340 --> 00:13:23,470
<font size="64">What is this?</font>

543
00:13:23,470 --> 00:13:25,540
<font size="64">Why does she look like that with only a straw?</font>

544
00:13:25,740 --> 00:13:29,350
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(It doesn't suit his taste, so he returns it right away.)</font>

545
00:13:28,450 --> 00:13:29,710
<font size="64">This is good.</font>

546
00:13:30,150 --> 00:13:32,550
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(They try the bun next.)</font>

547
00:13:32,550 --> 00:13:36,020
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Yummy!)</font>

548
00:13:38,290 --> 00:13:40,260
<font size="64">- It's so good! - This one?</font>

549
00:13:38,420 --> 00:13:40,490
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Eyes wide)</font>

550
00:13:40,390 --> 00:13:42,390
<font size="64">I like how the bingsu isn't too sweet.</font>

551
00:13:40,990 --> 00:13:44,760
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(He loves the bingsu.)</font>

552
00:13:42,390 --> 00:13:43,760
<font size="64">- You're right. - This is delicious.</font>

553
00:13:44,430 --> 00:13:45,560
<font size="64">- It's so good. - It's perfectly balanced.</font>

554
00:13:45,560 --> 00:13:46,600
<font size="64">You're right.</font>

555
00:13:47,500 --> 00:13:48,870
<font size="64">This is amazing.</font>

556
00:13:48,230 --> 00:13:52,440
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Even Dong Hyun, who was stressing about his allowance, is satisfied.)</font>

557
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:52,240
<font size="64">- It goes well with everything. - This is so good.</font>

558
00:13:52,740 --> 00:13:54,440
<font size="64">- I won't need a meal after this. - Seok Jin.</font>

559
00:13:52,870 --> 00:13:55,410
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Reasoning)</font>

560
00:13:55,310 --> 00:13:56,910
<font size="64">- This is as good as a meal. - Really?</font>

561
00:13:57,880 --> 00:14:00,140
<font size="64">I haven't had flavors this sophisticated in a while.</font>

562
00:14:00,140 --> 00:14:02,250
<font size="64">- It's really good. - Sophisticated flavors?</font>

563
00:14:01,510 --> 00:14:06,850
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(An elegant taste that won Mr. Free Meals over)</font>

564
00:14:02,250 --> 00:14:03,380
<font size="64">It's not too sweet.</font>

565
00:14:03,380 --> 00:14:05,050
<font size="64">We normally have it with condensed milk.</font>

566
00:14:05,050 --> 00:14:06,720
<font size="64">- I like that it's not too sweet. - You're right.</font>

567
00:14:06,780 --> 00:14:08,690
<font size="64">- I mean... - It's not overly sweet.</font>

568
00:14:08,690 --> 00:14:10,990
<font size="64">- It's packed with fruit. - Look at all this fruit.</font>

569
00:14:08,790 --> 00:14:11,020
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Wiping)</font>

570
00:14:11,760 --> 00:14:12,790
<font size="64">- Haha. - We won't get to have any.</font>

571
00:14:13,190 --> 00:14:14,330
<font size="64">- I'm sorry. - What is it?</font>

572
00:14:14,330 --> 00:14:16,790
<font size="64">I wiped my hands on this, thinking it was a wet wipe.</font>

573
00:14:16,790 --> 00:14:17,960
<font size="64">- Hey! - I'm sorry.</font>

574
00:14:18,200 --> 00:14:21,730
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(With oily bread crumbs)</font>

575
00:14:19,130 --> 00:14:21,070
<font size="64">- I'm sorry. - Isn't that a dishrag?</font>

576
00:14:21,270 --> 00:14:22,530
<font size="64">That doesn't look like a wet wipe.</font>

577
00:14:22,630 --> 00:14:24,740
<font size="64">- What got on there... - Are you kidding me?</font>

578
00:14:24,740 --> 00:14:26,600
<font size="64">I'm so sorry. I really am.</font>

579
00:14:25,040 --> 00:14:26,770
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Sniffing)</font>

580
00:14:26,940 --> 00:14:29,270
<font size="64">- The feeling of it... - It smells like pastries!</font>

581
00:14:29,410 --> 00:14:31,580
<font size="64">- No way. - No wonder he hates people.</font>

582
00:14:31,940 --> 00:14:33,110
<font size="64">I hate people.</font>

583
00:14:32,710 --> 00:14:34,140
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(I hate people.)</font>

584
00:14:33,340 --> 00:14:34,350
<font size="64">- He had his reasons. - Still, I like you.</font>

585
00:14:34,350 --> 00:14:35,710
<font size="64">I only like Nam Hyeong Ju.</font>

586
00:14:41,050 --> 00:14:42,690
<font size="64">Why is it called ube?</font>

587
00:14:42,950 --> 00:14:44,660
<font size="64">- I don't know. - You don't?</font>

588
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:46,360
<font size="64">That's the name of the plant.</font>

589
00:14:45,990 --> 00:14:49,060
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Ube: A purple yam commonly grown in Southeast Asia)</font>

590
00:14:48,790 --> 00:14:50,560
<font size="64">Mimi, do you know what late learner...</font>

591
00:14:50,560 --> 00:14:52,560
<font size="64">in "The Late Learner, Mr. Jee" means?</font>

592
00:14:52,560 --> 00:14:53,860
<font size="64">No, I don't.</font>

